      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented V&V suite. FDA internal QA procedures and DePuy Synthes simulation SOPs independently verified. All three modeling teams operate under ISO 9001-compliant quality systems. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
