      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual convergence criteria tightened to 1e-5 for force and displacement; energy criterion also monitored.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear solution used full Newton-Raphson with line search. Force residual converged to 1e-6 and energy residual to 1e-7 in all load steps. No divergence or bisection events observed across the 11-specimen ensemble. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
