      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon testing of same lot material; geometry from CMM measurements of tested specimens.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus obtained from tensile coupon tests on material from the same manufacturing lot as tested constructs. Rod geometry verified by CMM for each of the 11 specimens. Friction coefficients from pin-on-disk tribometry. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
