      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 specimens from production-representative lot; dimensional inspection confirms conformance to nominal geometry.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production components. Dimensional inspection of all 11 specimens confirmed conformance to drawing tolerances. Specimens split across two independent laboratories (6 and 5) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
