      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios or multiple ASTM F1717 configurations.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration only. No torsion, fatigue, or alternate offset conditions were included in this validation activity. This limitation reduces the achieved level to 2, one below the required level of 3. This shortfall is acknowledged and flagged for follow-on validation.",
