      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA input parameters directly traceable to physical measurements on the tested specimens.",
      "rationale": "Specimen-specific geometry (rod diameter, screw head offset, construct height) and material properties were measured and entered individually for each of the 11 FEA runs. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics. One-to-one correspondence between physical and virtual specimens confirmed. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
