      "rationale": "Validation constructs use the same 7.5 mm non-cannulated screw design, same PEEK rod, and same connector as the COU device. ASTM F1717 loading directly represents the worst-case compression-bending scenario for lumbar pedicle screw systems. Two-laboratory design strengthens generalizability. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
