    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged; however, the remaining factors collectively provide sufficient evidence that the FEA framework reliably predicts ASTM F1717 compression-bending behavior of the non-cannulated construct within the stated acceptance bounds. The assessment team accepts the model for the intended COU with the noted limitation on test condition coverage.",
